ite over 1200m at Wingatui last month. This is tougher, but she is capable of another bold showing. Each way. 2. VIVACIOUS opened her campaign with an easy win on a heavy track before finishing fifth on a good surface over 1400m here last time out. Stick with her, especially if it is wet. 5. AIRPARK HUSTLER was much better when finishing third at Riverton 7 days ago. He loves it here, and he can go one better.\",\"runners\":[3,1,11,2,5],\"exclusive\":true}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"NZ TAB","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,3,11,14]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,1,2,14]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[9,11,1,5]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,12,6,5]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,11,2]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,5,1,11]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,12,1,2]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,11,3,5]}],"dividends":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,"jackpotCarriedOver":0,"poolDividends":[{"selections":[1],"amount":3.4}]},{"wageringProduct":"Place","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,"jackpotCarriedOver":0,"poolDividends":[{"selections":[1],"amount":1.9},{"selections":[3],"amount":2.2},{"selections":[2],"amount":4}]},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,"jackpotCarriedOver":0,"poolDividends":[{"selections":[1,3],"amount":8.4}]},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,"jackpotCarriedOver":0,"poolDividends":[{"selections":[1,3],"amount":9.9}]},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,"jackpotCarriedOver":0,"poolDividends":[{"selections":[1,3],"amount":4.3},{"selections":[1,2],"amount":11.4},{"selections":[3,2],"amount":5.8}]},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","poolStatusCode":"Closed","countBackLevelDescription":null,